# Machine-specific secrets kept OUT of server/.env (that file is tracked
# in git — see NEW_GAME_PLAN.md's secret-hygiene note). This file itself
# (server/.env.local) is gitignored (*.local pattern).
# Kopyala: cp .env.local.example .env.local

# ── EWDS (Copernicus Early Warning Data Store) — used by glofas-importer ──
# Free personal account/token: https://ewds.climate.copernicus.eu
# Also requires accepting the cems-glofas-forecast dataset's licence at
# https://ewds.climate.copernicus.eu/datasets/cems-glofas-forecast?tab=download#manage-licences
# (live-verified 2026-07-22 — job submission 403s with a clear message
# until this is done, separate from having a valid API key).
EWDS_API_KEY=your-ewds-personal-access-token
